{"tid":426381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MK仔涉揮刀挾持阿伯飲可樂 見警即棄刀逃逸","createTime":"2017-10-06T14:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T08:26:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":96,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"f91e532352fecb2801804d5dd83a057513606e2e","tid":426381,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"較早前九龍城有人報案指一名赤膊男子持刀登上往旺角紅色小巴，聲稱去斬人殺人。而下午6時，旺角近鴉蘭街一名紮辮胖男子涉嫌揮刀挾持老伯飲汽水，見到軍裝警員後，立即丟棄一把開山刀，並向大角嘴方向逃逸。該男子很大可能與九龍城案件無關，但持刀原因暫時未明。<br />\n<br />\n警方將涉案開山刀及一罐汽水帶走調查，並派警犬搜捕。現場消息指，男子約40歲，胖身材、身穿藍色上衣、黑色褲、光頭、戴太陽眼鏡。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20171006/_2017100620165619603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20171006%2F_2017100620165619603.jpg&h=b111dc87&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n現場目擊者的士司機表示，他下午5時報警，見到持開山刀的紮辮胖男自言自語，並與附近街坊爭執，「你望乜X嘢呀」、「信唔信劈X埋你」。胖男並曾持刀挾持老伯，喝斥老伯飲用一罐由男子提供的汽水，老伯只好聽從。<br />\n<br />\n當時有軍裝警員剛好到場抄牌，的士司機指恐防警員不知男子有開山刀，於是提醒警員，警員立即追截，然後自己也逃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n的士司機更指，胖男案發時與另外2名男同黨一起，2名男同黨見勢色不對即逃去；而且胖男丟棄的開山刀與挾持老伯的開山刀不同，相信身上有多過一把刀。<br />\n<br />\n警方下午接報，報案人表示兩個男子在鴉蘭街和新填地街交界爭執，期間其中一名中年男子手持有毛巾包着的開山刀，指向報案人。兩名爭執的男子其後往塘尾道方向逃去。案件列作藏有攻擊性武器，由旺角刑事調查隊調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1031492/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1031492%2F&d=wHzxtsvRFk5DG64ZpVbQq%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=99c6f5ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1031492%2F&h=6860bd0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1031492/</a>"},{"pid":"8c9e99697894f85b8feff794d113d822a81c9fd2","tid":426381,"uid":14103,"like":83,"dislike":3,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:25:34.000Z","msg":"我個樣：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b2b0f3ef52c42a58c2e50b875cc00aa8643220","tid":426381,"uid":29540,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:27:17.000Z","msg":"心諗"},{"pid":"c370993367fe9168421c2ab408ef9d05702bf13a","tid":426381,"uid":85586,"like":157,"dislike":1,"score":156,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"逼人飲可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0719c8b07af2ac07257781f658b8c89f2c88ec","tid":426381,"uid":27396,"like":50,"dislike":12,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:27:32.000Z","msg":"啲廢老真係麻煩，請埋佢飲都要人迫扮可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ede3e4c22fb6139ba13b3c25b6cc5a05368cd2b","tid":426381,"uid":116530,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"揮刀挾持老伯飲汽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40e7ead47ab3c9ac19f8f563e53951afc9cdfe4","tid":426381,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8d8ca97cbf4b1a41b20370d3a21fd0a6af08ff","tid":426381,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>兩漢懷刀分別現身鬧市　警方正全力追緝</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n九龍城及旺角區分別出現懷刀危險人物，警方正全力展開追捕。一名手持逾呎長「七孔開山刀」男子下午出現廣東道鬧市，當與巡警相遇即棄刀逃去無蹤；另一名赤膊男子則持刀在城南道登上小巴，途人見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171006/s00001/71c6132900ed35bbc57c1ec966a2cfd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171006%2Fs00001%2F71c6132900ed35bbc57c1ec966a2cfd2.jpg&h=3cbd7ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171006/s00001/1507292262126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171006%2Fs00001%2F1507292262126&d=wHzxtsvRFk5DG64ZpVbQq%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b89d5312\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171006%2Fs00001%2F1507292262126&h=de0e1533\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171006/s00001/1507292262126</a></div><br />\n<br />\n旺角出現懷刀危險人物。事發下午5時許，當時有警員巡經廣東道近鴉蘭街時發現一名持刀可疑男子，男子看見警員即棄下利刀往大角嘴方向逃去，警員經追截無果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171006/s00001/71aa7bde971763f35502e1798b4338d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171006%2Fs00001%2F71aa7bde971763f35502e1798b4338d0.jpg&h=9b434748&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n事後警員封鎖現場調查，初步被遺棄地上的利刀為一把手柄包有紗布的逾呎長「七孔開山刀」，不排除有人正準備進行黑幫撕殺，因遇到巡警棄刀逃走；探員將利刀檢走作進一步化驗，正追緝一名年約40歲身材健碩男子、紥辮及戴太陽眼鏡、身穿有圖案短袖T恤及黑長褲。消息稱，現場附近有店舖閉路電視拍到與警方描述相似男子逃走片段，但未知是否屬同一人。<br />\n<br />\n另外在下午2時許，有市民在九龍城城南道，發現一名手持利刀赤膊中年男子在街上徘徊，暗中報警；惟警員到場前，可疑男子已登上一輛紅頂小巴往旺角方向離去。消息稱，警員到場調查期間再接報，早前區內一名男子，因事與家人爭吵後持刀外出，男子疑有暴力傾向及藏有攻擊性武器案底；警方正展開該名赤膊上身懷刀男子下落。"},{"pid":"ea7c698aa885557ec8e4002cf83c56b80b3365c5","tid":426381,"uid":102096,"like":89,"dislike":2,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:30:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02d2b86097cc65e53dd8498cff710991273cdfec","tid":426381,"uid":140626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"飲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e165225603f9a47f4c8d9e3ab45e315f9089121b","tid":426381,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"請人飲可樂係咪運盤桔慶祝人開張d fd"},{"pid":"761cfe9429f670aaa8e0aaa4b4b505fa51fc097a","tid":426381,"uid":103339,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xce80yr9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxce80yr9&h=40747fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同呢單新聞一鳩樣，睇完會黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0edd0a767d6dc052268e8770fe41f313506742","tid":426381,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"香港愈黎愈左痴線<br />\n之前地鐵放火 依家又周街飲可樂"},{"pid":"f73ab0607e3783c4878f1f3d46256dcceef1ee7b","tid":426381,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e87dbd16114e538cd51e69b1e4f51993367f2b","tid":426381,"uid":4811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試下呀!!"},{"pid":"043512b6ebf98a622ffabed3e7546195699e375b","tid":426381,"uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>紮辮男旺角持刀逼阿伯飲可樂　揚言出嚟冧友</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/223606_c7981e3b4a2e4b198c2861f34b6c351e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F223606_c7981e3b4a2e4b198c2861f34b6c351e.png&h=e0a9c80f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n旺角同一時間出現兩名持刀漢！在九龍城有人報案稱發現有男子懷疑持刀登上往旺角的小巴的同時，旺角亦有人報稱遭持刀漢「兇」，令人以為同一人所為，惟警方經初步調查，相信兩持刀漢並非同一人，現正分頭搜捕其歸案。<br />\n<br />\n曾在旺角目擊刀漢兇人之的士司機林先生，事後親述驚險過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。他表示，下午5時許，他在鴉蘭街路邊等候交更，期間見一名正在飲可樂的紮辮男，大搖大擺在街上行走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並疑與兩名男子對談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，由於他大吵大嚷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，語無倫次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，引起途人注視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，期間他突然向途經的老翁大喝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「你望乜X嘢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」然後從袋中取出一把開山刀指向老翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，再叫道：「我出嚟冧友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，信唔信我劈X埋你吖嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ！」<br />\n<br />\n林續稱，紮辮男向老翁遞上可樂稱：「你同我飲X咗罐汽水佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」當時老翁不敢亂動，只好發抖地接過可樂，默默喝下，期間兩名正在附近抄牌的軍裝警員，聞嘈吵聲前來了解，紮辮男見狀即時棄下一把開山刀，然後<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>奪回老翁手上的可樂</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，</span>向大角咀方向逃去，警員隨即展開追捕。林擔心警員及其他途人安全，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，疑犯其後再於附近街口將背囊及可樂棄下，警方連同開山刀檢走調查。但林指出，警方檢獲的開山刀，與他所見的並不相似，擔心其身上有不只一把刀。林又稱，當時附近途人都退避三舍，他亦慢慢退開，形容：「仲影相？我走都走唔切呀，佢揸住把刀追我咪X街！」<br />\n<br />\n至於九龍城的懷疑持刀漢，有目擊者發現他手持利刀登上前往旺角的小巴，更揚言「殺人」、「斬人」，警方將此案列作藏有攻擊性武器處理，交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進，警犬亦奉召到場協助搜證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171006/bkn-20171006174552757-1006_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171006%2Fbkn-20171006174552757-1006_00822_001.html&d=wHzxtsvRFk5DG64ZpVbQq%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b453dfab\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171006/bkn-20171006174552757-1006_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"66586fa124e366c82bfdb2ce37c7da50bf4041ae","tid":426381,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096b57af31b64c55baaf9495a91c6b905eb73f9c","tid":426381,"uid":41974,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"逼人糖尿病，慘過即刻殺咗你"},{"pid":"81c655e2e79b74622a2a853642f3d45c05e7b2f9","tid":426381,"uid":4811,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/224244_e387833c63b6888ad5440e0930c83a60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F224244_e387833c63b6888ad5440e0930c83a60.jpg&h=999efed7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbd2e6de5193df93e26e9ee9434202517d45a4b2","tid":426381,"uid":128600,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逼人飲可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n殖入式廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f186a926b59cca0ceca6e5f1377cd550afade3a8","tid":426381,"uid":6752,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:44:21.000Z","msg":"耐人尋味"},{"pid":"1f4771ae05df7a58b07ad5b2c8f1f7ae0e5a0831","tid":426381,"uid":35420,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"傻人發現案"},{"pid":"367679369150ffca8eeb296579d13bdfc639cb64","tid":426381,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd488ba6e3b58bc761fd07df2f869fab327cb9f3","tid":426381,"uid":4545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7368e9812f0a5e556d81f6b70ac650a4af903ec7","tid":426381,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":