-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/235249_7545ce65be84133414063aac98b8cd13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F235249_7545ce65be84133414063aac98b8cd13.jpg&h=c22556bc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個post好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5bed2cbf7ca0be4c1989fbc0bd68b3ba5ceec2","tid":426381,"uid":129658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:26:42.000Z","msg":"叫你飲就飲啦，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c03c79efa091f5fcc22b3251729282e095849f","tid":426381,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"可樂公司打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5159ad8cb25660286f28a7bb357ef93561286f","tid":426381,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a76e3dfd3e5e66b109de1c4bf2b9972154c35789","tid":426381,"uid":90123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:42:59.000Z","msg":"好混亂"},{"pid":"805f5a15002a8bf90ff9167543e93104fec55a79","tid":426381,"uid":25971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當時有軍裝警員剛好到場抄牌，的士司機指恐防警員不知男子有開山刀，於是提醒警員，警員立即追截，<span style=\"color: red;\">然後自己也逃離現場</span>。<br />\n<br />\n暗黑兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n古惑仔一 ，大天二又係咁樣報寸隊𡃁坤出黎俾個差佬打靶"},{"pid":"5709500fe52dc3e3ed517cd3e0ed3f4bc980a5af","tid":426381,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cba362a8010f34b8a10e4d62164a2b2aa511f93","tid":426381,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e259e3893f126b57f9e3f11724cb4ed7ad49a727","tid":426381,"uid":133599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:53:13.000Z","msg":"嘩 又咩玩法?"},{"pid":"af82228128c12190b53270ae25a26c9c72bb1116","tid":426381,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"???"},{"pid":"9482458c940a251ed5da2245e7c938912e321724","tid":426381,"uid":3103,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>較早前九龍城有人報案指一名赤膊男子持刀登上往旺角紅色小巴，聲稱去斬人殺人。而下午6時，旺角近鴉蘭街一名<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紮辮</span></span>胖男子涉嫌揮刀挾持老伯飲汽水，見到軍裝警員後，立即丟棄一把開山刀，並向大角嘴方向逃逸。該男子很大可能與九龍城案件無關，但持刀原因暫時未明。<br />\n<br />\n警方將涉案開山刀及一罐汽水帶走調查，並派警犬搜捕。現場消息指，男子約40歲，胖身材、身穿藍色上衣、黑色褲、<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光頭</span></span>、戴太陽眼鏡。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20171006/_2017100620165619603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20171006%2F_2017100620165619603.jpg&h=b111dc87&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n現場目擊者的士司機表示，他下午5時報警，見到持開山刀的紮辮胖男自言自語，並與附近街坊爭執，「你望乜X嘢呀」、「信唔信劈X埋你」。胖男並曾持刀挾持老伯，喝斥老伯飲用一罐由男子提供的汽水，老伯只好聽從。<br />\n<br />\n當時有軍裝警員剛好到場抄牌，的士司機指恐防警員不知男子有開山刀，於是提醒警員，警員立即追截，然後自己也逃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n的士司機更指，胖男案發時與另外2名男同黨一起，2名男同黨見勢色不對即逃去；而且胖男丟棄的開山刀與挾持老伯的開山刀不同，相信身上有多過一把刀。<br />\n<br />\n警方下午接報，報案人表示兩個男子在鴉蘭街和新填地街交界爭執，期間其中一名中年男子手持有毛巾包着的開山刀，指向報案人。兩名爭執的男子其後往塘尾道方向逃去。案件列作藏有攻擊性武器，由旺角刑事調查隊調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1031492/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1031492%2F&d=wHzxtsvRFk5DG64ZpVbQq%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=99c6f5ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1031492%2F&h=6860bd0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1031492/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啫係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n還珠格格啲古裝風？<br />\n到底光頭定唔係光頭"},{"pid":"25b6d763bd877250e544e100d8b71da97bcef1fb","tid":426381,"uid":7370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"梗係知個阿伯有糖尿，所以逼佢飲可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c335107f045f4c796b4b2443a7c1f8b0504bc2","tid":426381,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"係咪暗號黎<br />\n阿伯一飲可樂就開拖"},{"pid":"c43f3983501ab4c70cd9c3d38ab4b60f10ab84ca","tid":426381,"uid":19432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:34:03.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5b5cb444dad282be6c0eb64276b21cbad809e0","tid":426381,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:46:17.000Z","msg":"迫啲老嘢飲可樂<br />\n想佢地糖尿病發作<br />\n真係好涼戈戈"},{"pid":"7426489e66067e065c6e2835e3842250332d5a32","tid":426381,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迫啲老嘢飲可樂<br />\n想佢地糖尿病發作<br />\n真係好涼<span style=\"color: red;\">薄<br />\n<br />\n口德+5</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 禁錯"}]}